down at the police station.

309
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:21,360
The big brown table
down at the police station?

310
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:23,320
It's the best we could find,
my lord.

311
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,960
And five-- All together, now.

312
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:28,480
ALL:
Assaulting a police officer.

313
00:15:28,520 --> 00:15:29,640
