Thank you.

314
00:15:29,680 --> 00:15:32,920
Call Police Constable Pan-Am.

315
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,520
Oh! Ow!

316
00:15:38,560 --> 00:15:41,880
In-- Into the witness box,
constable.

317
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:48,440
There will be plenty of time
for that later on.

318
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:52,800
Now, you are
Police Constable Pan-Am?

319
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:56,040
No, I deny that
to the last breath in my body.

320
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:58,760
Oh, sorry, yes.

321
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:02,040
Police constable,
do you recognize
the defendant?

322
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:04,360
No. Never seen him before
