324
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,520
I'd recognize him anywhere.

325
00:16:08,560 --> 00:16:10,120
Sorry, super.

326
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:11,840
Constable, uh, will you
please tell the court

327
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,600
