what happened?

328
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:15,160
Oh, yes!

329
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:22,320
I was proceeding in a
northerly direction up
Alitalia Street

330
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,520
when I saw the deceased

331
00:16:24,560 --> 00:16:27,320
standing at an upstairs window

332
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:30,120
