at the general public.

333
00:16:30,160 --> 00:16:32,320
She then took off her--

334
00:16:32,360 --> 00:16:35,920
Wait a tick. Wrong story.

335
00:16:37,160 --> 00:16:38,920
Oh, yes.

336
00:16:38,960 --> 00:16:40,400
There were three nuns
in a railway compartment

337
00:16:40,440 --> 00:16:42,080
and the ticket in--

338
00:16:42,120 --> 00:16:46,120
No? Anyway,
I clearly saw the deceased--

339
00:16:46,160 --> 00:16:48,120
-Defendant.
-Defendant. Sorry.

340
00:16:48,160 --> 00:16:51,400
Sorry, super.
I clearly saw the defendant

341
00:16:51,440 --> 00:16:55,040
doing whatever
he's accused of, uh,
red-handed.

342
00:16:55,080 --> 00:16:58,800
When kicked a caution,
he said:

343
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:02,120
"It's a fair.
Cop, I done it all.

344
00:17:02,160 --> 00:17:05,000
Right no. Doubt about. That."

345
00:17:05,040 --> 00:17:07,200
Then, bound as he was
to the chair,

346
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,200
he assaulted myself

347
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:12,680
and three other constables
