00:18:23,480 --> 00:18:25,320
ANNOUNCER:
<i>And now the Stock Market</i>
<i>Report</i>

371
00:18:25,360 --> 00:18:27,080
<i>by Exchange Telegraph.</i>

372
00:18:27,120 --> 00:18:29,000
Trading was crisp
at the start of the day

373
00:18:29,040 --> 00:18:31,160
