after an early gain

377
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:39,600
and stools remained anonymous.

378
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:42,240
Armpits rallied well
after a poor start.

379
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:44,320
Nipples rose dramatically
during the morning,

380
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:46,200
