and buttocks remained firm.

382
00:18:49,360 --> 00:18:52,200
Small, dark, furry things
increased severely
on the floor

383
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:54,120
whilst rude jellies wobbled
up and down

384
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,240
and bounced against
rising thighs,

385
00:18:56,280 --> 00:18:58,880
which had spread to all parts
of the country
by mid-afternoon.

386
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:00,960
After lunch, naughty things
dipped sharply,

387
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,400
forcing giblets upwards
with the nicky nacky noo.

388
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,960
Ting tang tong
rankled dithely,
little tipples pooped,

389
00:19:06,000 --> 00:19:07,840
and poppy things went pong.

390
00:19:07,880 --> 00:19:10,200
Gibble gabble gobble went
the rickety rackety
roo as the--

391
00:19:12,200 --> 00:19:14,160
Mm, that'll teach you
to be normal.

392
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,320
Oh!

393
00:19:16,520 --> 00:19:18,600
[FOOTSTEPS]

394
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:19,680
